data.description: Beautiful brick ranch with large, fenced yard in sought after location.  The home offers a large living room with fireplace, and a family room on each level.  Three spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths on the main level.  The huge kitchen could offer a dining area, if needed, but there is a formal dining room as well.  Newer hi-efficiency furnace and central air.  The roofing was replaced in 2016.  In the basement you will find tons of storage, a workshop area, large family room and large laundry with storage.  Also a cold storage area for canned goods.  The spacious yard has vinyl fencing, a burn pit area, and a shed with electric.  New windows as well. Laundry used to be on the main level in the kitchen area. Short walk to High School and football field. Owner motivated.
